    <intervention_name>enzastaurin</intervention_name>
    <description>1125 mg loading dose then 500 or 875 mg, oral, daily, 4 week cycles with patients evaluated after each cycle. The dose difference is for patients who are on enzyme-inducing antiepileptic drugs versus non-enzyme inducing antiepileptic drugs.</description>
